3
00:00:09,042 --> 00:00:11,945 line:-2
[Shobi] Welcome to the session
"Meet TestFlight on Mac."


4
00:00:11.979 --> 00:00:13.313 line:-1 align:center
I'm Shobi Vijayakumar,


5
00:00:13.347 --> 00:00:15.115 line:-1 align:center
TestFlight Engineering Manager.


6
00:00:15.148 --> 00:00:16.984 line:-2 align:center
I'm really excited
to share with you


7
00:00:17,017 --> 00:00:20,621 line:-2
about the amazing new
