00:10:14,381 --> 00:10:16,717 line:-2
I think you will enjoy
all the new features


220
00:10:16.750 --> 00:10:17.851 line:-1 align:center
added this year


221
00:10:17.885 --> 00:10:20.354 line:-2 align:center
and have an amazing
TestFlight experience.


